## Glossary

### Boxing Terms

| English | Korean | Definition |
|---------|--------|------------|
| Jab | 잽 | A quick, straight punch with the lead hand |
| Straight | 스트레이트 | A powerful straight punch with the rear hand |
| Hook | 훅 | A curved punch targeting the side of the opponent |
| Uppercut | 어퍼컷 | An upward punch targeting the chin |
| Guard | 가드 | Defensive hand position protecting the face and body |
| Stance | 스탠스 | The positioning of feet and body |
| Orthodox | 오소독스 | Right-handed stance with left foot forward |
| Southpaw | 사우스포 | Left-handed stance with right foot forward |
| Slip | 슬립 | Head movement to evade a punch |
| Duck | 덕 | Lowering the body to evade a punch |
| Footwork | 풋워크 | Movement and positioning of the feet |
| Reach | 리치 | The distance a boxer can extend their punch |
| Clinch | 클린치 | Holding the opponent to prevent punching |

### Technical Terms

| English | Korean | Definition |
|---------|--------|------------|
| Pose Estimation | 포즈 추정 | Technology that detects body position from video |
| Stamp | 스탬프 | A marked key moment in the video |
| Coordinate | 좌표 | XYZ position data for body joints |
| Analysis | 분석 | AI-generated review of performance |
| Metric | 지표 | Measured performance indicator |
| Report | 리포트 | Complete analysis document |

### Metric Definitions

| Term | English Definition | Korean Definition |
|------|-------------------|-------------------|
| Reach-to-Distance Ratio | How well you maintain optimal punching distance | 최적의 펀칭 거리를 유지하는 정도 |
| Guard Recovery Speed | Time to return guard position after punching | 펀치 후 가드 자세로 돌아오는 시간 |
| Upper Body Tilt | Angle of torso lean during punches | 펀치 시 상체 기울기 각도 |
| Punch Frequency | Number of punches per minute | 분당 펀치 횟수 |
| Defense Rate | Percentage of time in defensive posture | 방어 자세 유지 비율 |
